## Project Structure

```
CyberBotChat/
├── CyberChatBot.slnx          ← Solution file
├── CyberBotChat/
│   ├── CyberChatBot.csproj    ← Project file (.NET Framework 4.7.2)
│   ├── App.xaml               ← Application entry point
│   ├── App.xaml.cs            ← App code-behind
│   ├── MainWindow.xaml        ← GUI layout (WPF XAML)
│   ├── MainWindow.cs          ← UI logic and bubble rendering
│   ├── Class1.cs              ← ChatbotEngine: all chatbot logic
│   └── Voice_message.wav      ← Voice greeting audio file
```

